# count numbers

### Brute force Approach
```
    public static int countDigits(int n) {
        // 'cnt' to store the count of digits.
        int cnt = 0;
        // While loop iterates until 'n is greater than 0'
        // becomes 0 (no more digits left).
        while (n > 0) {
            cnt = cnt + 1;
            // Divide 'n' by 10 to
            // remove the last digit.
            n = n / 10;
        }
        return cnt;
    }
```


